```plantuml
@startuml onprem_foundry

package "Foundry System" {
    [Furnace] as Furnace
    [Object Storage] as ObjectStorage
    [AUR] as AUR

    component "Builder Interface" {
        [Builder] as Builder
        [MakepkgBuilder] as MakepkgBuilder
        [BuilderWithMetrics] as BuilderWithMetrics
    }

    component "gRPC Service" {
        [furnacepb] as furnacepb
    }

    component "Package Management" {
        [pkgMap] as pkgMap
        [buildQueue] as buildQueue
    }

    component "Monitoring" {
        [Prometheus] as Prometheus
        [pprof] as pprof
    }

    component "CLI" {
        [Cobra] as Cobra
    }
}

Furnace --> furnacepb : exposes
Furnace --> Builder : uses
Builder <|-- MakepkgBuilder : implements
Builder <|-- BuilderWithMetrics : decorates
Furnace --> pkgMap : manages
Furnace --> buildQueue : processes
Furnace --> AUR : fetches packages
Furnace --> ObjectStorage : uploads packages
Furnace --> Prometheus : reports metrics
Furnace --> pprof : provides profiling
Cobra --> Furnace : controls

@enduml
```